<li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/spl/hi/pop_ups/05/europe_muslim_veils/html/1.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/spl/hi/pop_ups/05/europe_muslim_veils/html/1.stm" rel="nofollow">BBC drawings of different types of Islamic women's clothing</a></li>
</ul>
