<p><a name="Contemporary_Muslim_opinion" id="Contemporary_Muslim_opinion"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Hijab&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26" title="Edit section: Contemporary Muslim opinion">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Contemporary Muslim opinion</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://islamicweb.com/beliefs/women/albani_niqab.htm" class="external text" title="http://islamicweb.com/beliefs/women/albani_niqab.htm" rel="nofollow">Niqab is not required</a></li>
<li><span class="PDFlink"><a href="http://www.salafimanhaj.com/pdf/SalafiManhaj_TheLastStraw.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.salafimanhaj.com/pdf/SalafiManhaj_TheLastStraw.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Last Straw!</a></span><span style="font-size:smaller;"><a href="/wiki/Portable_Document_Format" title="Portable Document Format">PDF</a>&#160;(251&#160;<a href="/wiki/Kibibyte" title="Kibibyte">KiB</a>)</span></li>
</ul>
